--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Academic Use Only
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   This dataset is available for academic research purposes only. Any
   commercial use, in whole or in part, is strictly prohibited.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. No Redistribution Without Permission
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   You may not redistribute, republish, or share the dataset in any form
